This paper focuses on modeling source code vocabulary for machine learning, which is a topic that falls under software engineering (cs.SE) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the impact of modeling choices on performance, which is a common concern in machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with programming languages (cs.PL) and uses neural language models (cs.AI).
